<P>
   &UR;  &LR; MERRY CHRISTMAS TO ALL!
</P>
<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   BETHLEHEM-2000 (Bethlehem, West Bank) _ In the place where Jesus
was born, Christians from around the world celebrate the Christmas
that will usher in the third millennium of the faith. By Charles M.
Sennott. 1200 words.
</P>
<P>
   CANADA-TERRORISTS (Montreal) _ Individuals linked to an apparent
conspiracy to smuggle bombmaking materials and terrorist operatives
into the United States have been monitored for years by Canadaian
intelligence service. &UR;  &LR; By Colin Nickerson. 1000 words.
</P>
<P>
   CHECHNYA-MILITIA (Grozny) _ The Russian plan for the fall of
