<TEXT>
<P>
   ALL BUDGETED STORIES HAVE MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   Recapping:
</P>
<P>
   The following were eliminated from tonight's NYTNS budgets:
</P>
<P>
   HOUSTON-BABIES (Houston)
</P>
<P>
   SCI-SHUTTLE (Houston)
</P>
<P>
   N.Y. Times News Service.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
