<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-24 21:30 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8623 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-OBIT-FIGUEIREDO-NYT &LR;      12-24 1259
