</P>
<P>
   Mesa Air Group planned to repurchase 10 percent of its common
stock to bolster its shares.
</P>
<P>
   Hong Kong Stocks Soar
</P>
<P>
   Lifted by Thursday's record session on Wall Street, the Hang
Seng Index rose 537.20 points, to close at 16,833.28.
</P>
<P>
   Deadbeat Diplomats in New York City
</P>
<P>
   At any given time, several diplomatic offices in New York are
having financial difficulties. In their darkest hours, countries
often stop paying rent without permission.
</P>
<P>
